Routes:

Register route: http://localhost:3000/auth/register

Login route : http://localhost:3000/auth/login

Logout route : http://localhost:3000/auth/logout

Refresh-Token route : http://localhost:3000/auth/refresh-token

Steps to create Auth app

- Create an express app
- Establish routing
- Connection to MongoDB using mongoose
- create a user schema
- handling the request/response in auth.routes.js to register a new user
- Validating the email/password using JOI schema validation.
- Hashing passwords using bcrypt before saving it to the DB
- Introducing JWT access token